# Web App Rules

## MUST
- Build the user-facing PWA only.
- Use Next.js App Router and mobile-first layout.
- Use bottom navigation on mobile with only Home, Search, Watchlist, and Me.
- Use TanStack Query for server data.
- Use Zustand only for transient UI state.
- Use types from `packages/types`.

## MVP ROUTES
- `/`
- `/home`
- `/feed/[id]`
- `/search`
- `/narratives`
- `/narratives/[slug]`
- `/watchlist`
- `/me`
- `/login`
- `/settings/notifications`

## FORBIDDEN
- No admin-only UI in the web app.
- No dark theme.
- No Narrative bottom tab.
- No direct imports from `apps/admin`.
- No duplicate API DTOs.
